{"tid":671104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國殲20隱身不怎樣？ 印度：普通雷達就找的到","createTime":"2018-05-20T00:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T04:05:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":259,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"87b8ff97ee0ba92d092707ecd3217ea5387a8bf0","tid":671104,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:00:36.000Z","msg":"殲20隱身不怎樣？ 印度：普通雷達就找的到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Rq342ET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRq342ET.jpg&h=e96b70a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸殲20戰機是世界第4種具有匿蹤性能的戰機，不過印度卻表示「普通雷達就可發現殲20」。(圖/新華網)<br />\n<br />\n大陸自行設計與研發的殲-20戰機，是除了美國F-22、F-35，俄國Su-57以外的第4種匿戰鬥機。然而，據印度的說法「它並不怎麼特別，普通雷達也看的到」。<br />\n<br />\n俄國衛星網報導，印度空軍表示，殲20曾經在西藏空域進行飛行訓練，而印度就趁著這個機會，派出Su-30MKI戰機)對離邊界不遠的殲20嘗試搜尋，結果能夠有效追踪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LdlMdsG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLdlMdsG.jpg&h=3dffdc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度說，Su-30MKI的雷達就能發現殲20的行踪。中國大陸也有Su-30，稱為Su-30MKK，絕對可以自己驗證印度說法的真偽。(圖/印度空軍)<br />\n<br />\n印度空軍司令奧雅普拉哈(ArupRaha)說：「大陸的新飛機畢竟不是那麼隱身，我們的Su-30戰機雷達可以看到它們，雷達其中沒有什麼特殊的改裝，顯然普通雷達站也可以檢測的到。」<br />\n<br />\n殲20是成都飛機公司所研發製作的，據信自2002年開始開發，並使用大陸所掌握的匿蹤技術，包括蒙皮材質、內在彈艙。一般認2017年3月進入少數服役階段，最近剛成功完成了第一次海上訓練演習任務。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180520000050-260417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180520000050-260417&d=JJx%2BhOoRaLnw80yk8FS4fV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b65f1a4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180520000050-260417</a>"},{"pid":"d3a7958111084443c291bfa2619662df5d6ed8f9","tid":671104,"uid":28351,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:02:34.000Z","msg":"又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce65b4b529e8eabdae78a0db786de1f4b55eaf7","tid":671104,"uid":132859,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:03:55.000Z","msg":"根本係部加咗個彈倉嘅四代半機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a915b4e2db6bb57be519b286526bd829bc7edaeb","tid":671104,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e83071ef71bec2972d2771b60960d70d42e0811","tid":671104,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:07:02.000Z","msg":"中時<br />\n反了"},{"pid":"b98bdd62ce0938cff07e04e7e2a01d63fce9b169","tid":671104,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff6f00c0f7bb751c1af4508d7c0b92ad10f65b7","tid":671104,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03181a6130443c5787e2b896981a42e9e8c02d4c","tid":671104,"uid":135767,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64c4507fa1912b48025525546f186fed3b7635e5","tid":671104,"uid":46245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:18:41.000Z","msg":"簡單講句，係裝多個引擎既j10罷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96236cf0d373595cf50269cfdc3ee37df15bc8d6","tid":671104,"uid":12449,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:23:10.000Z","msg":"啲錢都俾人貪曬去 仲邊會有錢整飛機"},{"pid":"859e1d54d59bb3a17e1f1a9704a66bd94c7359f4","tid":671104,"uid":25424,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"可能支那自己雷達真係睇唔到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁先係真正既災難"},{"pid":"b95685d75b8e7ecdb8269f4faec44fe5af6ed682","tid":671104,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:37:34.000Z","msg":"共軍匿蹤戰機殲-20將繞台？國防部：來就抓得到<br />\n<br />\n中共解放軍昨日宣布共軍首款匿蹤戰機殲-20將在近日首次展開海上方向實戰化軍事訓練，國防部發言人陳中吉今天表示，國軍對台海周邊海空域任何動態情資都有能力掌握。將領則表示，國軍防情系統對中國大陸東南沿海升空的戰機都有能力掌握，加上遍布的防空飛彈警戒系統，殲-20若加入共軍「遠海長航」繞台行列，不管是單機或編隊，國軍都有能力加以掌握，若接近我防空識別區，國軍會派機升空緊跟監偵。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍今年以來已派出多批次戰機、轟炸機、預警機組成編隊進行繞島巡航，日前發布轟-6K的宣傳片中，甚至高調出現101大樓畫面，因此殲-20首次出海很可能是台海方向。而根據新浪看點報導，殲-20今年首先裝備的作戰部隊可能有3支，分別是滄州飛行訓練基地、東部戰區空軍「王海大隊」所在旅，以及最新出現的空軍山東半島某基地。坊間關切，若殲-20雙機單獨繞台巡航，若在我方戰管未發現下，被拍下背景為蘭嶼、綠島或南大武山的巡航照片，將難以對國人交待。兩岸匿蹤戰機對雷達，誰會先看見誰？考驗我監偵戰備能力。<br />\n<br />\n對此，陳中吉表示，國軍針對台灣周邊海空狀況充分監偵，國軍對台海周邊海空域任何動態情資都有能力掌握。<br />\n<br />\n將領則表示，空軍長程預警雷達與戰管系統的能量，基本上共軍戰機自東南沿海機場甫升空，國軍就掌握得到，包括殲-20。任何共機接近我防空識別區，國軍機隊會依既有戰備程序，升空緊跟監偵。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/3134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F3134&d=JJx%2BhOoRaLnw80yk8FS4fV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c4045154\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/3134</a>"},{"pid":"c6c467511133dfca235d42090280646ea2e04193","tid":671104,"uid":99205,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:43:08.000Z","msg":"大陸乜撚都係抄，預左流架啦"},{"pid":"2ff64d15e24001f050883908789e1f55e86b2ce1","tid":671104,"uid":107269,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"859e1d54d59bb3a17e1f1a9704a66bd94c7359f4","tid":671104,"uid":25424,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"可能支那自己雷達真係睇唔到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁先係真正既災難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:43:15.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗😂😂"},{"pid":"e535793faa3debe71bea85aac5b9aa60b8346ca3","tid":671104,"uid":51127,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"跟本就得個樣，實際上只係一部普通國產垃圾，好耐之前已經有人話佢連個外型都跟本唔合臉乎隱形條件，特別係機頭個隻前翼，而且中國跟本無能力生產真正的隱形物料........<br />\n<br />\n引擎，航電，雷達，武器系統，全部都係垃圾，只係一部放大左既玩具模型<br />\n<br />\n不過打平民應該夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71230019fdcd2fb51944b2c01ffec3dc27b93fd2","tid":671104,"uid":22736,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"中國只有騙子是真的"},{"pid":"f843d309f89b34939322734db75566c2cd1c2a51","tid":671104,"uid":60787,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:07:00.000Z","msg":"殲20啲機師係咪好似賭俠咁不斷唸：<br />\n你睇我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0813d78737eca27217ff271d9d0487ed6a8b64","tid":671104,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"印度空軍司令沙哈（Arup Shaha）表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">蘇-30雷達</span>能抓到解放軍最新的隱形戰機，可見其匿蹤能力不太行。"},{"pid":"f43a17021dff06251ca120229858e384a76d3dae","tid":671104,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03181a6130443c5787e2b896981a42e9e8c02d4c","tid":671104,"uid":135767,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd9ed09505d1d934a4418c3c7337bdd5fe4dfc9","tid":671104,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"859e1d54d59bb3a17e1f1a9704a66bd94c7359f4","tid":671104,"uid":25424,"like":190,"dislike":1,"score":189,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T00:27:30.000Z","msg":"可能支那自己雷達真係睇唔到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"